                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18380514-1318-offence-1 t18380514-cd-162"></join>30th of April</rs>, 71/4 lbs. weight of lead pipe, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 metal cock, value. 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18380514-name-995" type="victimName">
